tadata":174,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"Skadden, Arps, Slate, Meagher & Flom LLP",350,9845,"Optional Retirement Plan: Pursuant to the firm’s retirement agreement, as amended by my January 20, 2021 agreement with the firm, I am entitled to receive an early retirement cash payment if I retire from the firm between the ages of 57 and 62. The payment will be equal to 1.5 times the amount of my annual firm income. To calculate my annual firm income, Skadden  will take the average of the firm’s expected income in the fiscal year in which I retire and the firm’s income in the two fiscal years preceding my retirement. This payment shall be paid ratably over the 84 months following my retirement. (2021-03-01)",{"description":171,"appointee_id":33,"dsid":87,"endnote":7,"entity_id":172,"id":176,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":43,"metadata":177,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},9841,"401K Savings Plan: I will continue to participate in this defined contribution plan. The firm will not make further contributions after my separation. (1997-07-01)",{"description":171,"appointee_id":33,"dsid":87,"endnote":7,"entity_id":172,"id":179,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":64,"metadata":180,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},9844,"Defined Contribution (Keogh) Retirement Plan: I will continue to participate in this defined contribution plan. The firm will not make further contributions after my separation. (2021-03-01)",{"description":171,"appointee_id":33,"dsid":87,"endnote":7,"entity_id":172,"id":182,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":92,"metadata":183,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},9842,"Capital Account: Pursuant to the partnership agreement, I will receive the balance of the capital account within two years of my withdrawal date. The payment will be calculated as of